That's what you said
to me, right mom?

00:17:51.638 --> 00:17:53.106
That that's the trick.

00:17:55.776 --> 00:17:56.810
Look right now,

00:17:56.844 --> 00:17:58.612
I seriously want
to stop the fight

00:17:58.645 --> 00:17:59.613
between you and dad,

00:17:59.646 --> 00:18:01.915
that started 'cause of me.

00:18:01.949 --> 00:18:04.484
I know I haven't been
able to completely

00:18:04.518 --> 00:18:06.153
master this jutsu.

00:18:06.186 --> 00:18:08.322
I always mess up
halfway through,

00:18:08.355 --> 00:18:11.558
'cause I can't seem to
overpower my opponent's will.

00:18:14.928 --> 00:18:17.030
But one time dad told me,

00:18:17.064 --> 00:18:19.299
when he was in trouble
a long time ago,

00:18:19.333 --> 00:18:22.002
you saved him with
mind transfer.

00:18:22.035 --> 00:18:24.638
The jutsu, passed down
through the Yamanaka clan.

00:18:26.573 --> 00:18:28.876
I wanna master the
mind transfer jutsu,

00:18:28.909 --> 00:18:30.043
and make it my own,

00:18:30.077 --> 00:18:31.678
so that I can help everybody.

00:18:33.947 --> 00:18:35.148
Inojin.

00:18:41.788 --> 00:18:43.557
He stopped aunt Ino.

00:18:45.792 --> 00:18:46.994
Uncle Sai,

00:18:48.529 --> 00:18:51.198
okay so, (whispers)

00:18:51.231 --> 00:18:52.900
What? you mean here and now?

00:18:52.933 --> 00:18:53.901
Well if you don't,

00:18:53.934 --> 00:18:55.669
then this isn't going to end.

00:18:56.670 --> 00:18:58.005
I guess you're right.

00:18:58.038 --> 00:18:59.406
Yeah, of course I am.

00:19:03.510 --> 00:19:05.279
It's okay now Inojin.

00:19:18.058 --> 00:19:21.061
So what exactly happened?

00:19:21.094 --> 00:19:23.030
All's well that
ends well I guess.

00:19:23.063 --> 00:19:25.899
And it's thanks to your
mind transfer jutsu.

00:19:25.933 --> 00:19:27.100
Wait what?

00:19:39.046 --> 00:19:40.747
Anyway look at you Inojin,

00:19:40.781 --> 00:19:42.883
