use the jutsu on me.

00:19:42.916 --> 00:19:44.618
You said I was out of my league,

00:19:44.651 --> 00:19:46.019
and not to bother.

00:19:46.053 --> 00:19:48.155
Oh, well, no you did great.

00:19:48.188 --> 00:19:51.058
I could feel the strength of
your willpower surpass mine.

00:19:51.091 --> 00:19:53.460
It was a perfect
mind transfer jutsu.

00:19:53.493 --> 00:19:55.629
It looks like you've
figured it all out.

00:19:55.662 --> 00:19:56.630
Right dear?

00:19:56.663 --> 00:19:57.631
Don't you think?

00:19:57.664 --> 00:19:59.032
That's right.

00:20:05.506 --> 00:20:06.974
[Ino] I was surprised.

00:20:07.941 --> 00:20:09.142
How about you?

00:20:10.277 --> 00:20:11.745
Yeah.

00:20:11.778 --> 00:20:13.514
Well that ended up just great.

00:20:13.547 --> 00:20:15.649
I'll say.

00:20:16.550 --> 00:20:17.885
What's up?

00:20:17.918 --> 00:20:19.920
Tomorrow, I'll treat
you to a burger.

00:20:19.953 --> 00:20:21.655
Just like I promised you.

00:20:21.688 --> 00:20:23.490
Awesome. Thanks.

00:20:23.524 --> 00:20:24.892
Fries too.

00:20:24.925 --> 00:20:28.161
