00:20:28.195 --> 00:20:29.663
No shut up Chubs.

00:20:30.664 --> 00:20:32.266
Uh-huh there it is.

00:20:42.543 --> 00:20:43.544
[ Boruto] Are you serious?

00:20:43.577 --> 00:20:46.046
Yep that's right. That's
the way the two of us

00:20:46.079 --> 00:20:50.150
