00:20:52.653 --> 00:20:55.122
Yeah Well, I mean so what right?

00:20:58.192 --> 00:21:00.294
Cho-Cho, it's all yours.

00:21:00.327 --> 00:21:02.796
Oh yes. I'm going
to dig right in.

00:21:02.829 --> 00:21:03.797
Thanks.

00:21:03.830 --> 00:21:06.066
Hey Inojin, so I heard,

00:21:06.099 --> 00:21:09.002
