mind transfer jutsu.

00:21:09.036 --> 00:21:10.871
That's amazing.

00:21:10.904 --> 00:21:13.874
So can you give us a
little demonstration?

00:21:13.907 --> 00:21:17.044
What? No, I'm not going
to do it right here.

00:21:17.077 --> 00:21:19.513
Come on we just want a peak.

00:21:19.546 --> 00:21:20.747
Yeah, come on do it.

00:21:20.781 --> 00:21:21.748
Show them,

00:21:21.782 --> 00:21:23.016
they wanna see it.

00:21:23.050 --> 00:21:24.017
Like I said,

00:21:24.051 --> 00:21:25.285
I don't wanna.

00:21:28.222 --> 00:21:30.157
Oh, don't be such a meanie.

00:21:38.232 --> 00:21:40.767
Mind transfer Jitsu complete.

00:21:40.801 --> 00:21:42.636
Guess she's not
gonna to get to eat

00:21:42.669 --> 00:21:44.137
