00:21:45.506 --> 00:21:46.607
Inojin?

00:21:46.640 --> 00:21:48.008
So you switched?

00:21:48.041 --> 00:21:49.743
Yeah I finally did it.

00:21:49.776 --> 00:21:51.044
At last,

00:21:51.078 --> 00:21:53.347
I'm able to overpower Cho-Cho's
strong love for fries.

00:21:53.380 --> 00:21:54.515
Amazing.

00:21:55.449 --> 00:21:58.252
Well, I think that's
probably enough for now.

00:22:01.054 --> 00:22:03.290
Oh man, fries are so good.

